      <title>Iran's nuclear program set back 'a few months.' And, Trump to meet with NATO allies</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/06/25/g-s1-74499/up-first-newsletter-iran-nuclear-program-nato-summit-emil-bove</link>
      <comments>https://text.npr.org/2025/06/25/g-s1-74499/up-first-newsletter-iran-nuclear-program-nato-summit-emil-bove</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.npr.org/2025/06/25/g-s1-74499/up-first-newsletter-iran-nuclear-program-nato-summit-emil-bove</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Jun 2025 11:13:28 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div id="storytext" class="storytext storylocation linkLocation"&gt;       &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Good morning. You're reading the Up First newsletter. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/newsletter/news" target="_blank"&gt;Subscribe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt; here to get it delivered to your inbox, and &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/podcasts/510318/up-first/" target="_blank"&gt;listen&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt; to the Up First podcast for all the news you need to start your day.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;h3 class="edTag"&gt;Today's top stories&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A U.S. official, speaking on condition of anonymity, has informed NPR that the Defense Intelligence Agency believes the damage&lt;/strong&gt; to Iran's most important nuclear site, Fordow, was limited. According to the official, Iran's nuclear program has probably been &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/06/24/nx-s1-5444303/iran-nuclear-program-u-s-strikes-intelligence-assessment" target="_blank"&gt;set back by "a few months" or so&lt;/a&gt;. This is an early assessment by the DIA, and comes after President Trump claimed the U.S. air campaign against three Iranian nuclear sites destroyed Iran's nuclear program.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-74436-1" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 8275;         --source-height: 5407;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/8275x5407+0+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fd2%2F49%2F139f483646cfa3e37c6d7b2e875b%2F03-new-airstrike-craters-at-perimeter-installation-fordow-fuel-enrichment-facility-24jun2025-wvl.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/8275x5407+0+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%