      <title>Israel and Iran's fragile ceasefire. And, what to know about NYC's mayoral race</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/06/24/g-s1-74200/up-first-newsletter-israel-iran-ceasefire-nyc-mayoral-race-supreme-court-deportations</link>
