      <title>Trump leaves G7 to focus on Mideast conflict. And, Vance Boelter faces federal charges</title>
      <author>Suzanne Nuyen</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/06/17/g-s1-73103/up-first-newsletter-trump-g7-iran-israel-vance-boelter-charged-purdue-pharma-opioid-epidemic</link>
      <comments>https://text.npr.org/2025/06/17/g-s1-73103/up-first-newsletter-trump-g7-iran-israel-vance-boelter-charged-purdue-pharma-opioid-epidemic</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.npr.org/2025/06/17/g-s1-73103/up-first-newsletter-trump-g7-iran-israel-vance-boelter-charged-purdue-pharma-opioid-epidemic</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Jun 2025 10:36:59 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;div id="storytext" class="storytext storylocation linkLocation"&gt;       &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Good morning. You're reading the Up First newsletter. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/newsletter/news" target="_blank"&gt;Subscribe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt; here to get it delivered to your inbox, and &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/podcasts/510318/up-first/" target="_blank"&gt;listen&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt; to the Up First podcast for all the news you need to start your day.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;h3 class="edTag"&gt;Today's top stories&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;President Trump left the G7 summit one day early to focus on the rapidly escalating conflict between Israel and Iran. &lt;/strong&gt;The White House &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/06/16/nx-s1-5436119/trump-leave-g7-iran-israel" target="_blank"&gt;abruptly announced Trump's exit&lt;/a&gt; from the summit after the president posted a dire warning on social media telling Iranians to evacuate the capital, Tehran.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-73093" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 4876;         --source-height: 2743;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4876x2743+0+160/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F40%2Fef%2Ff7212f984097bf43005bebea723f%2Fgettyimages-2219803039.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4876x2743+0+160/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F40%2Fef%2Ff7212f984097bf43005bebea723f%2Fgettyimages-2219803039.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4876x2743+0+160/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F40%2Fef%2Ff7212f984097bf43005bebea